records.name: Lacasa Villa

descriptions.direction: Located in Ukulhas, Paguro Villa is near the beach. Folhudhoo Harbor and Ukulhas Harbor are local landmarks, and the area's natural beauty can be seen at Ari Atoll and Ukulhas Beach. Take an opportunity to explore the area for water adventures such as fishing.
descriptions.general: Set in Ukulhas, 200 metres from Ukulhas Beach, Lacasa Villa offers air-conditioned accommodation and a garden. This 3-star hotel offers a shared kitchen and room service. Staff on site can arrange airport transfers.
descriptions.other: This property will not accommodate hen, stag or similar parties.
